statements.subject: uim:ne/e0ee3094-bb7e-4719-be80-2de5bf96f16c
statements.object: Semantic Ink is combining a cloud service for handwriting recognition with an entity recognition, linking ink with semantic concepts from either a public or personal knowledge graph.

statements.subject: uim:ne/767a402a-b8cc-476d-86d1-89f36247308b
statements.object: Refers to technology that digitally represents handwriting in its natural form. In a typical digital ink system, a digitizer is laid under or over an LCD screen to create an electromagnetic field that can capture the movement of a special-purpose pen, or stylus, and record the movement on the LCD screen. The effect is like writing on paper with liquid ink. The recorded handwriting can then be saved as handwriting or converted to typewritten text using handwriting recognition technology.
